        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-6 group-hover:text-color-accent transition-colors text-black">Power Plants & Distribution Substation (Civil Works)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-light leading-loose mb-8 pr-4 text-black">
            Complete services from planning to maintenance. Focus on precision and safety. Vital utility infrastructure supporting power distribution across the region.
